Description
This seed file captures the UUID sending us abnormal usage ping counters. Those UUID are excluded from the analytics downstream models in order to allow easy charting. For example in [this issue](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-data/analytics/-/issues/4343), one can clearly see an abnormal spike in monthly numbers of `projects_prometheus_active`.
